At the age of 26, I carry the burden of three previous speeding incidents on my driving record, resulting in accumulated penalty points. I recognize the significance of these prior transgressions and their impact on my driving history. I am determined to reflect upon these mistakes and make the necessary changes to ensure that I exercise better judgment on the road going forward.

